Disini step-by-setp untuk instalasi jasper report untuk LinovCloud di Centos 6.6

1. Pastikan java-1.7.0-openjdk sudah terinstall
   # instalasi java -> goo.gl/vxruKf
2. Pastikan apache tomcat sudah terinstall
   # instalasi tomcat -> https://goo.gl/dnL9LS <rekomendasi tomcat v6>

Step-by-step setting jasper report

2. Copy file Javabridge.war ke webapps
3. copy additional lib ke C:\Program Files\Apache Software Foundation\Tomcat 7.0\webapps\JavaBridge\WEB-INF\lib
   Setting environmentnya di Path-> System variables -> new "JAVA_HOME" variable value = "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_75"
   Setting environmentnya di Path-> System variables -> Edit -> Variable value = "C:\xampp\php" 
	
4. Pastikan di environment variable PATH sudah di setting untuk mengarahkan ke folder PHP


Problem Solve :
1. Jika masih error, required url allow: php.ini url_allow_ = on
   # edit file php.ini -> gedit /etc/php.ini
   # allow_url_include = off -> allow_url_include = on
   # restart httpd
2. Download JavaBridge.war untuk centos 6.6
   # goo.gl/6B2gL7
   # 
